    "While only the more dominant techniques were represented in the graph, it could be clearly observed that a myriad of AI techniques were adopted and applied in recent years across different papers to uncover hidden ESG driven insights.",
    "Multivariate regression (and its various regularized or ensemble forms) continued to dominate, especially for papers looking to evaluate relationships between ESG and non-ESG attributes.",
    "This was followed by natural language processing techniques, which were useful to inspect semi-structured or unstructured alphanumeric ESG-related datasets.",
    "Page 31 of 64 76",
    "The analyses above provide researchers insights into how each research archetypical domain can differ in terms of the application of AI techniques."
